phonology 中文翻譯
發音：  名詞複數:phonologies   
中文翻譯手機版n.1.音位學；音韻學。2. 語音學〔主指語音的歷史研究〕。n.-gist 音位學家；音韻學家。addressed phonology:    查找到的語音直呼語音autosegmental phonology:    自分音系理論computational phonology:    計算聲韻學english phonology:    英音系; 英語音系學firthian phonology:    弗斯音系學generative phonology:    生成音位學; 生成音系學german phonology:    德音系; 德語音系學lexical phonology:    詞匯音系學linear phonology:    線性音系學metrical phonology:    節律音系學natural phonology:    自然語音系統學on phonology in jinghuayuan:    韻學談prelexical phonology:    前詞典語音加工russian phonology:    俄語語音學segmental phonology:    分節音韻學suprasegmental phonology:    超音段音位swedish phonology:    瑞典語發音; 瑞典語音系學vietnamese phonology:    越南音系; 越南語音系學archaic chinese phonology:    上古音aue australian english phonology:    澳洲英語語音學historical chinese phonology:    漢語音韻史; 漢語音韻學multi-level phonology:    多層次音系學non-linear phonology:    非線性音系學old chinese phonology:    古音phonolysis:    聲解作用phonologist:    音韻學者
